<li>1760–70&#160; <a href="/wiki/William_Baker_(British_politician)" title="William Baker (British politician)">Sir William Baker</a><sup id="cite_ref-199" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-199">&#91;199&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li>1770–82&#160; Sir Bibye Lake, Jr.<sup id="cite_ref-200" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-200">&#91;200&#93;</a></sup></li>
