<li>1799–1807&#160; Sir James Winter Lake<sup id="cite_ref-202" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-202">&#91;202&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li>1807–12&#160; William Mainwaring<sup id="cite_ref-203" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-203">&#91;203&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li>1812–22&#160; Joseph Berens<sup id="cite_ref-204" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-204">&#91;204&#93;</a></sup></li>
