<li>1852–56&#160; <a href="/wiki/Andrew_Wedderburn_Colvile" class="mw-redirect" title="Andrew Wedderburn Colvile">Andrew Wedderburn Colvile</a><sup id="cite_ref-206" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-206">&#91;206&#93;</a></sup></li>
