<li>1874–80&#160; <a href="/wiki/George_Goschen,_1st_Viscount_Goschen" title="George Goschen, 1st Viscount Goschen">George Joachim Goschen</a><sup id="cite_ref-211" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-211">&#91;211&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li>1880–89&#160; <a href="/wiki/Eden_Colvile" title="Eden Colvile">Eden Colvile</a><sup id="cite_ref-212" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-212">&#91;212&#93;</a></sup></li>
