<li>1925–31&#160; Charles Vincent Sale</li>
<li>1931–52&#160; Sir <a href="/wiki/Patrick_Ashley_Cooper" title="Patrick Ashley Cooper">Patrick Ashley Cooper</a> – first governor to visit HBC operations in Canada.<sup id="cite_ref-216" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-216">&#91;216&#93;</a></sup></li>
